Legend has it that there is an island that exists in a different dimension, a place where reality is distorted and the laws of physics do not apply. This island is said to be home to creatures that were created by human emotions, and the dominant emotions on the island are greed, anger, and sadness.

It is said that the island was discovered by a group of sailors who were lost at sea. They stumbled upon the island by accident, and were immediately entranced by its beauty. However, as they explored the island, they began to notice that something was not quite right.

The island was inhabited by strange creatures that seemed to be made out of pure emotion. These creatures were born from the feelings of the people who had been stranded on the island over the years, and they had taken on a life of their own.

In Dinosaur World Mobile, you start as a small dinosaur and research bigger and stronger dinosaurs in order to increase your chances of survival as you explore the world and interact with others.

The new Ecosystem game mode allows you to experience an ecosystem of dinosaurs in their respective habitats, with a food chain consisting of a range of carnivores, herbivores and omnivores. Food is limited and dinosaurs must either fight or scavenge to survive; Ecosystem mode is ideal for realistic gameplay.

- Hunt for food and manage your hunger, thirst and sleep
- Research dinosaurs to unlock stronger ones
- Customise your appearance
- Make friends or fight your enemies

This game has been heavily optimised for mobile, tablet, and computer devices.

MPS Futsal is an exciting, fast-paced game!
In MPS Futsal, you play in a small arena with opposition and teammates, like in soccer/football, using a few tools to interact with the ball.

MPS Futsal is based on as its name implies, Futsal and soccer.
Futsal is a faster-paced version of soccer/football, typically played on a smaller field with fewer players than regular soccer/football.
This results in a faster-paced game, more exciting, and more goal-scoring opportunities than regular soccer/football.

Please consider liking and favoriting MPS Futsal, as it helps us out immensely as a small game.

Welcome to the wonderful world of Ants! In this exciting Roblox game, you get to experience the life of an ant, from crawling around the nest to foraging for food and defending your colony against enemy insects.

As a new ant in the colony, you'll start out by performing simple tasks such as gathering food and building tunnels. But as you gain experience and earn rewards, you'll be able to take on more challenging tasks like exploring new areas, fighting off predators, and even expanding your colony by recruiting new ants.

The game features a realistic, immersive environment where you can encounter a variety of creatures, both friendly and hostile. You'll need to use your skills and strategy to navigate the terrain, avoid dangers, and work together with your fellow ants to achieve your goals.

With stunning graphics and engaging gameplay, Ants is the perfect game for anyone who loves strategy, adventure, and the natural world. So what are you waiting for?

One person is made Simon, the others are the contestants. Standing in front of the playing area, Simon tells players what they must do while facing the many rounds upcoming. However, the contestants must only obey statements that begin with the words "Simon says." You can customize the board in VIP servers! (Note that wins don't count in them)
If you don't want to beat the tutorial, go play in a VIP server.
Exploiting of any sorts is NOT allowed in this game, and you will be punished for it.

How to play:
The board is divided into tiles, with mines randomly distributed.
To win, you need to step on all the safe tiles, without stepping on a mine.
The number on a tile shows the number of mines around it in a 3x3 area.
Using this information, you can determine tiles that are safe, and tiles that contain mines.
Tiles suspected of being mines can be marked with a flag using the left mouse button.
